{"id":687325,"date":[{"year":1984,"month":11,"day":20}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"215","ytitle":"","mtitle":"听朱明瑛唱歌","ftitle":"","authors":["刘宏远"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘宏远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一忽儿是非洲姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一忽儿是印度少妇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚刚穿西方衣裙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又着上东方长袍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你唱着英语，印地语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿拉伯语，斯瓦希利语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管我不懂外国语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那又有何妨?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我确实听懂了你唱的歌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻译出来只有一句话:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“生活啊，多么美好!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象淙淙流水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似春风拂面；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比夜莺婉转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比黄鹏清脆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你唱着一支支生活之歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声在长空荡漾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就象插上了翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻盈地越过山川湖海；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既没有语言障碍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也没有洲际国界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活的歌声，优美的旋律，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缩短了不同肤色的距离。"}]}